data.description: Gorgeous all brick end-unit townhouse impeccably maintained by the original owners. Upscale open floor plan with primary bedroom on the main, 2-story great room with fireplace and built in cabinetry. Private covered front porch and veranda off the great room. 2 upstairs bedrooms each with private bath and spacious loft living area overlooking great room. 2 car oversized garage with storage space, half bath and bonus room. There is also a whole house filtered water system. All unattached furniture will be removed. Washer/Dryer stays with the property. Fantastic location convenient to shopping, and Lake Lanier is right across the street! Amazing picturesque views from back of the property.
